      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 49
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Available for the discerning collector is a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in showroom condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically optimized with a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement, the chassis rigidity and drivetrain harmonics are impeccable. Power is managed by a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and an M Variable Differential. The exterior retains its factory luster, while the interior displays zero bolster wear, reflecting its meticulously maintained history. A mechanically transparent, investment-grade driver\u2019s car.",
